    "long_instructions": "### Loud & Quiet\r\n\r\n**The Scenario:**\r\n\r\nImagine an artist wants a song that plays with extreme quiet and loud contrasts to build tension and excitement. Your job is to create a remix that highlights that dynamic range — not just with volume, but with timing and layers too.\r\n\r\n**Do This:**\r\n\r\n- Use volume settings to make some parts of your song whisper quiet and others bold and loud.\r\n- Sequence those shifts so they happen in a pattern — for example, a quiet part after every 8 beats.\r\n- Layer sounds with **rests** to emphasize when something cuts out or surges in.\r\n- Try using effects like filters or fades to make the volume transitions feel smoother or more dramatic.\r\n\r\n**Musical Suggestions:**\r\n\r\n- “Something Just Like This” – The Chainsmokers & Coldplay *(builds into explosive choruses from calm openings)*\r\n- “Tightrope” – Tinashe *(delicate moments mixed with big dynamic peaks)*\r\n- “Angel” – Halle *(soft vocals that can contrast beautifully with louder beats)*\r\n\r\n**To pass this level, your song must include at least 2 quiet sections and 2 loud sections, clearly sequenced and layered to show contrast using volume changes, rests, or effects.**",
    "display_name": "Loud & Quiet",
    "bubble_choice_description": "Help an artist create a song that plays with extreme quiet and loud contrasts to build tension and excitement.",
